com.primavera.common.value.spread

Interface EPSSpreadPeriod

  • All Superinterfaces:
    ProjectSpreadPeriod, SpreadPeriod, WBSSpreadPeriod

    public interface EPSSpreadPeriod
extends ProjectSpreadPeriod

    This interface defines all access methods for each EPS spread period. The spread period is calculated according to the bucket type.

    See WBSSpreadPeriod for documentation on specific methods.
